body.body: Home Button Operation for Models with TFT Instruments
On the above models, the HOME button will not operate if any messages in the information tray have not been acknowledged.

To acknowledge a message in the information tray, users must press the joystick button centre. If more than one message is displayed, push the joystick left/right to show and acknowledge the other messages.
When all messages have been acknowledged, the HOME button will now function as intended.
